-- Treasury to provide $5 billion in aid to auto suppliers
-- 
-- Thu Mar 19, 2009 11:22am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2009/03/19/us-autos-suppliers-bailout-idUSTRE52I4RB20090319

 

 WASHINGTON  (Reuters) - The U.S. Treasury on Thursday announced plans to provide $5 billion in aid to auto suppliers, sources said. 

 Highlights: * US Treasury to provide $5 billion in aid to auto suppliers- source * US government assistance to auto suppliers to flow through US automakers- source * US auto supplier aid program expected to take a few weeks to begin to implement- source